  "1812090": {
    "name": "Escape Academy",
    "steam_appid": 1812090,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/badd4e21dec70fa7433163201e963073.avif?t=1747087130\" width=616 height=135 /></span><br><br>你刚刚来到逃脱学院，一所旨在将学生训练成终极密室逃脱大师的学校。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/40a30d530f0675bf8d9ad549aceb1948.poster.avif?t=1747087130\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/40a30d530f0675bf8d9ad549aceb1948.webm?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/40a30d530f0675bf8d9ad549aceb1948.mp4?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游玩十几个精心制作的密室，全都由现实世界中经验丰富的密室逃脱专家精心设计。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/b88e1c2a6a565d612ff01eb1277339a3.poster.avif?t=1747087130\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/b88e1c2a6a565d612ff01eb1277339a3.webm?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/b88e1c2a6a565d612ff01eb1277339a3.mp4?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>可单人或两人组队游玩，完整体验《Escape Academy》的精彩内容。支持局域网联机或联网分屏游玩。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/ed60dfbabee0060bd14a11513b5d9a65.poster.avif?t=1747087130\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/ed60dfbabee0060bd14a11513b5d9a65.webm?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/ed60dfbabee0060bd14a11513b5d9a65.mp4?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>探索逃脱学院的校园，认识各位教职员工，这些个性鲜明的角色个个都是逃脱领域的好手。其中一些还有不为人所知的秘密……<br><br>由风格独特的Doseone操刀设计的游戏原声（Gang Beasts、SLUDGE LIFE、Disc Room、Enter the Gungeon的作曲家）。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/7991a927b878094e79fe966f3ee19382.avif?t=1747087130\" width=616 height=135 /></span><br><br>在《Escape Academy: Tournament of Puzzles》中，直面约阿奇教练的挑战！与好友一决高下，在全球各地进行解谜竞赛！ <br>本次重大内容更新包括三种大型竞技赛、三种新游戏模式、谜题增强、额外成就以及超多全新谜题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/99d4d9e87090c89d37901a712a853d9c.poster.avif?t=1747087130\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/99d4d9e87090c89d37901a712a853d9c.webm?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/99d4d9e87090c89d37901a712a853d9c.mp4?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在可反复游玩的超大竞技赛中解谜，去发现并探索竞技赛中设置的秘密通道和备用路线。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>逃脱大师之墓 - 深入埃及腹地，踏上第一段逃脱之旅。在幽深墓穴的秘密通道中解开迷题，可别不小心成为这里的永久居民！<br></li><li>骇客谜影 - 废弃的鱼罐头厂成为了骇客们的天堂。这个潮湿多雨的码头充满了科技与水产主题的惊人谜题。<br></li><li>雪人工作室 - 准备好成为谜题的一部分吧！在最大的逃脱谜题中面对数不胜数的神奇挑战！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/30003f2c9d88d48f78d5c6617f2ab432.poster.avif?t=1747087130\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/30003f2c9d88d48f78d5c6617f2ab432.webm?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/30003f2c9d88d48f78d5c6617f2ab432.mp4?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>逃脱竞赛 - 与好友进行一场解谜竞赛，看看谁才是解谜大师。<br></li><li>井字棋 - “X”和“O”都被锁起来了，你又该如何赢下这经典游戏呢？<br></li><li>寻宝游戏 - 寻找谜题的答案，同时别忘了寻找宝物。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/ad060505a838aa544b94924d3b1a3823.poster.avif?t=1747087130\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/ad060505a838aa544b94924d3b1a3823.webm?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812090/extras/ad060505a838aa544b94924d3b1a3823.mp4?t=1747087130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果还嫌不够刺激，那么《Tournament of Puzzles》还提供了全新的谜题增强！布置陷阱分散对手的注意力，或是利用协助获取优势，最终赢得胜利。<br><br>更喜欢单人逃脱解谜？没问题！约阿奇教练教练很乐意让所有逃脱大师们在单人模式下解开他的谜题。就算解谜，也要熟能生巧！<br><br>我们为有胆量来挑战的逃脱大师们准备了不少古怪（偶尔还会致命）的“惊喜”，而以上提到的这些，仅仅是这些惊喜的冰山一角。你还在等什么？<br><br>赶快来解开迷题，逃出生天吧！",
